<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Enquiry submited @Bundle-Media</title>
</head>
<style>
    *{
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: sans-serif;
    }
    .parent{
        width: 50%;
       border: 1px solid black;
       margin: auto;
       display: flex;
       flex-direction: column;
       align-items: center;
       justify-content: center;
       padding-bottom: 15px;
    }
    img{
        display: block;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        margin: 15px auto;
    }
    .tableBox{
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 40px;
        padding: 20px 0px;
    }
    table,tr,td{
        border: 1px solid;
    }
    td,th{
        padding: 10px 0px;
    }
    td{
        width: 50%;
    }
    tr>td:last-child{
        padding: 15px;
    }
     .horizontal{
        border-bottom: 1px solid black;
        width: 100%;
        height: 1px;
    }
 
</style>
<body>
    <div class="parent">
        <img src="https://bundle-media.co/public/images/logo.jpg" alt="Bundle-Media">
        <div class="tableBox">
        <div class="first-child">
            <p>Dear Team,</p>
            <p>You have received a new enquiry with below details.</p>
        </div>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>Name:</td>
                    <td>{{fullname}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Email:</td>
                    <td>{{email}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Link your youtube channel:</td>
                    <td>{{youtubeChannel}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Usual length of the final edited video:</td>
                    <td>{{videoLength}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>A perfect example video which represents the style of editing you are looking for:</td>
                    <td>{{whatLookingFor}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>What is your frequency of uploads in a month:</td>
                    <td>{{freq}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>What is your budget:</td>
                    <td>{{budget}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Discord ID:</td>
                    <td>{{discord_id}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Let us know about any other services you are looking for too:</td>
                    <td>{{information}}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
         <p>Feel free to reach out to us at info@gent.care for any quries.</p> 
